[SPEECH town_Moonglow]

ON=*zoo*
	IF ( <COMPLEXITY.HIGH> || <COMPLEXITY.MEDIUM> )
		DORAND 3
			SAY We closely examine everything, both natural and arcane. The zoo that is to the south of Moonglow provides much materials for the study of animal lore.
			SAY We are too busy to wander through the wilderness to view animals in their native habitat. The zoo to the south of Moonglow provides us with much information on the natural fauna.
			SAY If it were not for the zoo in southern Moonglow, the mages would have to trek into the wilds to view these humble creatures ... and grass stains make for angry apprentices.
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 3
			SAY The zoo is south of central Moonglow.
			SAY The zoo is south of the city.
			SAY If it wasn't for the zoo in southern Moonglow, the mages would have to trek into the wilds to look at these animals.
		ENDDO
	ENDIF
ON=*graveyard*
ON=*cemetery*
	IF ( <COMPLEXITY.HIGH> || <COMPLEXITY.MEDIUM> )
		DORAND 3
			SAY Moonglow's graveyard is just north of the zoo. It is the way of things that everyone, even mages, must return to the natural cycle.
			SAY The cemetery is found to the south of the city. It is a small one, but strikingly serene.
			SAY Our graves are located to the south of the city. There are not many, for when magical research goes awry, there is usually not enough left to intern ....
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 3
			SAY Moonglow's graveyard is north of the zoo.
			SAY The cemetery is south of the city.
			SAY Our graves are down south of the city.
		ENDDO
	ENDIF
ON=*mag*guild*
	IF ( <COMPLEXITY.HIGH> || <COMPLEXITY.MEDIUM> )
		DORAND 3
			SAY Indeed, Moonglow has several Mages' Guilds. Three in fact. One to the south, one to the east and one to the north.
			SAY The three Mages' Guilds can be found scattered about the city's skirts. If thou hast questions concerning quests or other such magic subjects, they are a good place to begin asking questions.
				SAY The Mages' Guilds are places those learned in the magic arts gather. If thou hast questions, any of the three are equally knowledgeable. At least two are within easy distance of a teleporter.
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 3
			SAY Moonglow's got lotsa Mages' Guilds. One's down south, one's out east and one's up north.
			SAY The three Mages' Guilds are all 'round the city's edge.
				SAY At least two Mages' Guilds are within easy distance of a teleporter.
		ENDDO
	ENDIF
ON=*apprentice*
	IF ( <COMPLEXITY.HIGH> || <COMPLEXITY.MEDIUM> )
		DORAND 3
			SAY Each Mages' Guild has an assigned apprentice living nearby.
			SAY There is one apprentice for each Mages' Guild. Therefore, one is to be found near the northern Guild, one near the southern Guild, and one to the east.
			SAY Do not be shy of approaching the mages' apprentices. They live near the Mages' Guilds. Apprentices are busy, but rarely so involved as to be unhelpful.
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 3
			SAY Each Mages' Guild's got an assigned apprentice living nearby.
			SAY There's one apprentice near the northern Guild, one near the southern Guild, and one to the east.
			SAY Mages' apprentices live near the Mages' Guilds.
		ENDDO
	ENDIF
ON=*professor*
ON=*mag*teacher*
ON=*teach*mag*
ON=*mage*
	IF ( <COMPLEXITY.HIGH> || <COMPLEXITY.MEDIUM> )
		DORAND 3
			SAY Moonglow is full of master mages. Perhaps more than half a dozen, and they can all answer knowledgeably about arcane matters. I'd give thee directions, but they move about throughout the day.
			SAY If thou hast a question concerning magic, find a master mage - a professor at the Lycaeum, for instance. They can be touchy at home, but are usually affable during class hours.
			SAY Master mages are usually professors at the Lycaeum. They can be found there, or in their homes, or sometimes about the streets of Moonglow. They are usually willing to answer questions.
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 3
			SAY Master mages walk around all day.
			SAY Master mages are touchy at home, but usually talkative during class hours.
			SAY Master mages are found at the Lycaeum, or in their homes, or sometimes around on the streets of Moonglow.
		ENDDO
	ENDIF
ON=*teleporter*
	IF ( <COMPLEXITY.HIGH> || <COMPLEXITY.MEDIUM> )
		DORAND 3
			SAY Moonglow is a grand, vast city, and 'twould be problematic to walk from hither to yon all day. We've four teleporter locations, not counting the one in the center of the city.
			SAY Teleporters? Well, there's one near the Lycaeum, of course, one by the zoo, one near the eastern residence section, and one near the northern houses.
			SAY We've put a teleporter at each of the far flung edges of town: zoo and Lycaeum, and then the two residential areas.
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 3
			SAY We got four teleporter locations, not countin' the one in the center of the city.
			SAY Teleporters? There's one near the Lycaeum, one by the zoo, one over near the eastern housing section, and one near the northern houses.
			SAY We got a teleporter at each of the edges of town: zoo and Lycaeum, and then the two housing areas.
		ENDDO
	ENDIF
ON=*telescope*
	IF ( <COMPLEXITY.HIGH> || <COMPLEXITY.MEDIUM> )
		DORAND 3
			SAY Moonglow got its start, thou knowest, by studying the moons' manipulation of the ether. Our telescope furthers our education about the sky. If thou wishes to see it, head to the easternmost of the city.
			SAY Thou canst guess from our city's name that our scholars are intrigued by celestial objects. In the eastern part of the city, near the shore, we have the realms' largest eyeglass pointed at the sky.
			SAY There are certainly some schools of magic that ignore the heaven's influence, but in Moonglow it is studied intensely. Our telescope was custom made to scry for those things of most interest to mages.
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 2
			SAY Our telescope is over in the east part of the city.
			SAY In the eastern part of the city, out near the shore, we got a telescope.
		ENDDO
	ENDIF
ON=*gadget*
	IF ( <COMPLEXITY.HIGH> || <COMPLEXITY.MEDIUM> )
		DORAND 3
			SAY Moonglow is not restricted to the study of magic. We have one of the Gadgeteers' Guilds in the heart of the city.
			SAY If thou art interested in finding the Gadgeteers' Guild, look in the main part of the city, toward the southeast.
			SAY The Gadgeteers' Guild is in the heart of the city, to the southeast of the teleporters.
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 3
			SAY Our Gadgeteers' Guild's in the heart of the city.
			SAY The Gadgeteers' Guild's in the main part of the city, toward the southeast.
			SAY The Gadgeteers' Guild's in the heart of the city, over southeast of the teleporters.
		ENDDO
	ENDIF
ON=*town hall*
ON=*city hall*
	IF ( <COMPLEXITY.HIGH> || <COMPLEXITY.MEDIUM> )
		DORAND 3
			SAY If thou'rt looking for the town hall, look to the southwest corner of the heart of Moonglow.
			SAY Town hall is  a short walk southwest of the main teleporters.
			SAY Town hall is in the city proper, just south of the butcher and herbalist's shops.
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 3
			SAY Town hall is to the southwest corner of the heart of Moonglow.
			SAY Town hall is southwest of the main teleporters.
			SAY Town hall is in the middle of the city, south of the butcher and herbalist's shops.
