		DORAND 3
			SAY The best place in Moonglow to buy supplies would be at the provisioner's shop, just south of the docks.
			SAY I buy my supplies at the provisioner's shop. Thou'lt find him betwixt the baker and tailor.
			SAY If thou'rt looking to buy supplies, look around the north part of the commercial section of Moonglow. The provisioner is north of the woodcrafter.
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 3
			SAY The provisioner's shop is just south of the docks.
			SAY Thou'lt find the provisioner 'twixt the baker and tailor.
