		DORAND 3
			SAY We have an excellent woodcrafter in Moonglow, just south of the provisioner's shop. The skill of the craft is no doubt influenced by the nearby Art Guild.
			SAY We do indeed have a woodcrafter. Look between the provisioner and the reagent store.
			SAY Thou should stop and take a look at the woodcarver's wares. Thou'lt find the store just north and a bit west from the main teleporter location. The skill and detail work are, I think, second to none.
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 3
			SAY The woodcrafter is south of the provisioner's shop.
			SAY Look between the provisioner and the reagent store for the woodcrafter.
			SAY The woodworker's near the main teleporter location.
		ENDDO
	ENDIF
