	IF ( <COMPLEXITY.HIGH> || <COMPLEXITY.MEDIUM> )
		DORAND 3
			SAY Our tailor has a central location, just across the street from the provisioner.
			SAY If thou hast a need for new garb, thou'lt find our tailor in the center portion of Moonglow, just west of the inn.
