	IF ( <COMPLEXITY.HIGH> || <COMPLEXITY.MEDIUM> )
		DORAND 3
			SAY Fine armour can be had from the armoury in the center of town. Look to the west of Moonglow, to one side of the street that leads west out of town.
			SAY The armourer is neighbor to the healer. They have a friendly rivalry, and jest about which service does a soldier more good.
			SAY Thou canst find an armourer in the center of Moonglow. For all this is a city of study and research, the armourer's old fashioned methods still bring a decent living.
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 3
			SAY The armoury is near the center of town.
			SAY The armourer is neighbor to the healer.
			SAY Thou can find an armourer in the center of Moonglow.
		ENDDO
	ENDIF
