	IF ( <COMPLEXITY.HIGH> || <COMPLEXITY.MEDIUM> )
		DORAND 3
			SAY Herbs can be found in the city, west and south of the teleporters.
			SAY There is an herbalist in the city proper, in case thou'rt interested in the natural arts. The store is frequented most often by mages who dabble in the gentler of magics.
			SAY The herbalist is found but one door south of the shop of reagents. Theirs customers are similar, but their businesses do not conflict as often as thou might suspect.
